Method Detail

setReadOnly

public void setReadOnly(boolean readOnly)
Sets this properties widget to read-only. All ui fields will be set to read-only. Currently this only works if you set the MetadataProperties to read-only. If you try to set it back to not read-only the add/remove panel won't be re-added. We don't need this functionality at the moment so I haven't implemented it.

readOnly -
